•

Here’s a dope YouTube video I just dropped on building wealth & creating Family S.O.P’s
•

Family Standard Operating Procedures are the guidelines that easy family should have in place so that the generations that follow have the actual blueprint to sustain wealth.
•

What usually happens is, one generation acquires the wealth through learning the rules to the game & making the investments.
•

Then they usually pass the wealth to the next generation who saw the grind so they may appreciate it.
•

But by the 3rd generation,there’s no ties to the struggle, their entire life is on a silver platter, wealth is normalize, but there’s no blueprint to keep it & no reference point for them to look back on and say this is where we come from.
•

Go check out the full YouTube clip on Family S.O.P’s on my YouTube Channel.
•

node.text:
As leaders & Educators we must understand that we all will come under great scrutiny. And our people have that right.
•

They have been lied to, scammed, mislead & sometimes ruined from bad experiences.
•

It’s easy for us to say, how can u not know that was a scam? Why didn’t you use common sense?
•

Well, when you’re in survival mode, it ain’t always easy to see things for what they are.
•

Sometimes you go against your better judgement because you want a sense of relief.
•

A many times in my life i risked my life and freedom because is wanted relief.
•

Our people have trauma on so many levels, we must remember to show them the way, not shame them or belittle them.
•

We must have compassion & patience at all times.
•

It’s a long journey ahead, but there’s truly freedom on the other side. And if we are serious about leading them there (no matter what our method is) we must always show up as leaders.
•

I challege us all to give more and more value to the culture, to the community. Go out our your way to show up and push your limits on education.
•

I do know there’s more love than hate, our community has always searched for leadership. And the dope part is, They don’t care if you’re not perfect.
•

They will follow you, but only if you walk with them & not ahead of them.
•

When You walk amongst them, they will fight for you & not against you.
•

True leadership is always about The PEOPLE!!
•

To anyone who i have ever been impatient with on this journey, I apologize for that. I was still  developing as a leader.
•

I still am, but as i grow i hope u all see how i am evoling to represent those who rock with me Well.
•
